What do you need ?
------------------
For compile, use Lazarus 0.98.2 with Synabse 39 or above.

Note : Synabse 39 not supporte Win64 compilation. Use trunk version or lasted
version.

Configure
---------
In ftpconfig.inc, you can conigure if you application is GUI (must be set to
update all visual component).

You can define type of list server Unix (TYPE_SERVER_UNIX) or Windows
(TYPE_SERVER_WINDOWS).
You can simulate a Windows FTP server on Unix or Unix FTP server on Windows, as
you want.